cast.overview: In the future, an outbreak of canine flu leads the mayor of a Japanese city to banish all dogs to an island used as a garbage dump. The outcasts must soon embark on an epic journey when a 12-year-old boy arrives on the island to find his beloved pet.
cast.title: Isle of Dogs

details.biography:
Alex Orman is a 22 year old british actor known for Isle of Dogs, also known as a youtube personality, with a channel name Alex but also known as Craftedrl. Alex Orman's YouTube channel currently has 1.8 million subscribers and almost 400 million views as of July 7, 2018

He is currently apart of the youtube channel The Pals, The Pals consists of the youtube personalities DenisDaily with 5.6 million subscribers, Sketch with 1.7 million subscribers, Corl with 1.1 million subscribers, Sub with 1.5 million subscribers, and Flebsy with almost 10 thousand subscribers.
details.name: Alex Orman
